	<Coords points="945,2386 1491,2386 1491,2421 1471,2421 1471,2492 1480,2492 1480,2545 1490,2545 1490,2579 1477,2579 1477,2631 1443,2631 1443,2700 1516,2700 1516,2734 1438,2734 1438,2806 1489,2806 1489,2850 1484,2850 1484,2889 1430,2889 1430,2973 1445,2973 1445,3007 1024,3007 1024,3047 893,3047 893,3015 894,3015 894,2953 893,2953 893,2856 894,2856 894,2746 893,2746 893,2700 894,2700 894,2642 893,2642 893,2597 894,2597 894,2441 945,2441"/>
	<TextEquiv>
	<Unicode>People are very good at detect-
ing this and separating the com-
mitted wheat from the rhetorical
chaff. Too much of the latter and
people stop believing and invest-
ing in change initiatives of any
sort. They adopt compliant behav-
iors and work on the window-
dressing aspects while continuing
to attempt to provide the organi-
zation with what they think it
really wants as evidenced by its
actions.</Unicode></TextEquiv>
